Interface Parameter

ParameterImpl
public interface Parameter
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject

A representation of the model object 'Parameter'.

The following features are supported:

  • Data Type
  • Data Type Notes
  • Name
  • Name Notes
  • Semantics
  • Semantics Notes

isAvailableFrom

boolean isAvailableFrom(InteractionClass interactionClass)
Tests if this parameter is available from the given interaction class. An available parameter is defined as follows: The set of declared parameters of an interaction class in union with the set of inherited parameters of that interaction class. (See section 3.1.5 in IEEE 1516.1-2000)

Parameters:
interactionClass - the interaction class to be tested
Returns:
true if this parameter is available from the specified interaction class, false otherwise.
